OL,3,CAmerican singer D4vd arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering teenager
OL,6,FAmerican singer D4vd has been arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of killing of a 14-year-
OL,8,Fold girl whose body was found in the
OL,9,Fboot of his car seven months ago.
OL,11,FLos Angeles police said in a statement
OL,12,Fthat detectives arrested the alt-pop
OL,13,Fsinger and TikTok star, whose legal
OL,14,Fname is David Burke, on suspicion of
OL,15,Fmurder in the investigation of the
OL,16,Fkilling of Celeste Rivas Hernandez.
OL,18,FThe 21-year-old is being held without
OL,19,Fbail, and a case will be presented to
OL,20,Fprosecutors on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
