OL,3,CAmerican singer D4vd arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering teenager
OL,6,FBurke's attorneys said in a statement
OL,7,Fthat he is innocent.
OL,9,FHis defence lawyers said: "Let us be
OL,10,Fclear ` the actual evidence in this
OL,11,Fcase will show that David Burke did
OL,12,Fnot murder Celeste Rivas Hernandez and
OL,13,Fhe was not the cause of her death."
OL,15,FThey added: "There has been no
OL,16,Findictment returned by any grand jury
OL,17,Fin this case and no criminal complaint
OL,18,Ffiled. David has only been detained
OL,19,Funder suspicion. We will vigorously
OL,20,Fdefend David's innocence."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
