OL,3,CAmerican singer D4vd arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering teenager
OL,6,FPolice said investigators would
OL,7,Fpresent a case to prosecutors at the
OL,8,FLos Angeles County District Attorneys
OL,9,FOffice on Monday.
OL,11,FThe office said in its own statement
OL,12,Fthat it is aware of the arrest and its
OL,13,FMajor Crimes Division will review the
OL,14,Fcase to determine whether there is
OL,15,Fenough evidence to file charges.
