OL,3,CAmerican singer D4vd arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering teenager
OL,6,FThe singer had been under
OL,7,Finvestigation by an LA County grand
OL,8,Fjury looking into the death of Rivas
OL,9,FHernandez.
OL,11,FAlthough the probe was meant to remain
OL,12,Fconfidential, it became public on
OL,13,FFebruary 25 when members of Burke's
OL,14,Ffamily filed an objection in a Texas
OL,15,Fcourt to subpoenas demanding they
OL,16,Ftestify.
OL,18,FAuthorities did not publicly name
OL,19,FBurke as a suspect until his arrest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
