OL,3,CAmerican singer D4vd arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering teenager
OL,6,FThe body of Rivas Hernandez was found
OL,7,Fin a Tesla towed from the Hollywood
OL,8,FHills on September 8, a day after she
OL,9,Fwould have turned 15.
OL,11,FShe was a 13 when her family reported
OL,12,Fher missing in 2024 from her hometown
OL,13,Fof Lake Elsinore, about 70 miles
OL,14,Fsoutheast of Los Angeles.
OL,16,FThe 2023 Tesla Model Y in which the
OL,17,Fbody was found was registered in the
OL,18,Fsinger's name at the Texas address of
OL,19,Fhis subpoenaed family members,
OL,20,Faccording to court filings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
