OL,3,CAmerican singer D4vd arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering teenager
OL,6,FIt had been towed from an expensive
OL,7,Fneighborhood in the Hollywood Hills
OL,8,Fwhere it had been sitting, seemingly
OL,9,Fabandoned.
OL,11,FD4vd, pronounced David, gained
OL,12,Fpopularity among Generation Z fans for
OL,13,Fhis blend of indie rock, R&B and lo-fi
OL,14,Fpop.
OL,16,FHe went viral on TikTok in 2022 with
OL,17,Fthe hit "Romantic Homicide," which
OL,18,Fpeaked at No. 4 on Billboard's Hot
OL,19,FRock & Alternative Songs chart.
