OL,3,CAmerican singer D4vd arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering teenager
OL,6,FWhen the body was discovered, D4vd had
OL,7,Fbeen on tour in support of his first
OL,8,Ffull-length album, Withered.
OL,10,FLater, the last two North American
OL,11,Fshows, in San Francisco and Los
OL,12,FAngeles, along with a scheduled
OL,13,Fperformance at LA's Grammy Museum,
OL,14,Fwere canceled, as was the European
OL,15,Ftour that was to have begun in Norway.
